title: About
text: This is Aliscyn Hammond’s Sport Blog.This blog is about all my curious findings about basketball at all levels, from grassroots to the pros. Through a combination of written content and visual graphics, I aim to highlight the stories, strategies, and culture that make the game so special. Whether you’re a player, coach, or fan, my goal is to bring you closer to the game with insightful analysis and creative visuals that capture the essence of basketball and giving more knowledge to those who are interested in the sport!
